#Marco Rodriguez User Stories Based on Elicitation Responses

Story 1: As a customer, I need the ability to securely pay a small deposit or save a card on file during the booking process, so that I can guarantee my appointment slot and the store can reduce no show rates.

Story 2: As a store manager, I need the system to require all customers to register their pet details before finalizing a booking, so that our staff is fully prepared for the specific size and needs of the animal arriving.

Story 3: As a product owner, I need the booking system to enforce unique capacity rules and time blocks for grooming, training, and boarding, so that we never overbook our physical kennel space or trainer availability.

Story 4: As a customer, I need to be able to cancel or reschedule my appointment online, so that I can adjust my plans while the system automatically applies any necessary 24 hour cancellation fees or deposit forfeitures.

Story 5: As a returning customer with a registered account, I need to view my past appointments and saved pet profiles, so that I can quickly rebook my favorite services with just a few clicks and receive personalized recommendations.

Story 6: As a product owner, I need a reporting dashboard that tracks the online booking conversion rate, so that I can measure exactly how many customers successfully complete the online flow compared to manual scheduling.

#Sheridan Dela Cruz User Stories on Elicitation Responses (I ranked them as a start)

Story 1. Online Appointment Scheduling (Priority 1)
As a customer, I need to schedule grooming, training, or boarding appointments online so that I can book services at any time without calling the store.

Story 2. Service Selection (Priority 2)
As a customer, I need to choose the specific service my dog needs so that I can book the correct appointment type.

Story 3. Calendar & Time Slot Selection (Priority 3)
As a customer, I need to view available dates and times so that I can select an appointment that fits my schedule.

Story 4. Groomer Daily Schedule View (Priority 4)
As a groomer, I need to see my scheduled appointments for the day so that I can prepare for each pet and manage my workload.

Story 5. Pet Profile Updates (Priority 5)
As a customer, I need to update my petâ€™s profile information so that groomers have accurate details before the appointment.

Story 6. Groomer Notes & Behavior Logging (Priority 6)
As a groomer, I need to log pet behavior and service notes so that future appointments are informed by past experiences.
